cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Kairos in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "Kairos — the AURA dual-process trading brain"
abstract: >-
  Kairos fuses a strictly-causal System-1 order-book microstructure
  perception engine (LOB-Core) with a System-2 multi-agent LLM reasoning
  firm (TradingAgents) over a Causal Perception Bus, closing the backtest
  look-ahead hole by construction rather than by review.
type: software
